{"tid":736913,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"【Orage台】街霸打 Day225 10/7","createTime":"2018-07-10T14:57:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T17:22:34.000Z","uid":122942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eec246b8b98d8db799cf93ac4c6f712c277543b0","tid":736913,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T14:57:54.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/5ADqP2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2F5ADqP2.gif&h=8c5a58f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大家好，我係Orage。 我會於每晚11點至2點開台玩遊戲同與觀眾聊天。<br />\n因為我極度3分鐘熱度，所以好少會一直玩同一隻Game。<br />\n有興趣嘅巴打入黎捧下場，一齊傾下計啦  <br />\n<br />\n今晚11點左右見 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Foragejan%20&d=OKhsXWmyEKM7vwdGwXkoYJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=7424e462\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/oragejan </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i2/W4CK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi2%2FW4CK8P.png&h=69cccb5f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另外我開左個FB專頁，有時會PO日常野同覺得有趣嘅事，<br />\n希望巴打們可以入黎比個讚。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/oragejan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Foragejan&d=OKhsXWmyEKM7vwdGwXkoYJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=cfbf8e95\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/oragejan</a></div>"},{"pid":"93c6a96d4a59cd1f165e21ebfcc60685fa8e9be9","tid":736913,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"已開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8543f4b5ce916eba96470e0b9279e9e9f3da32","tid":736913,"uid":122942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-10T15:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814082399d9267f7a28f9685d401424fdb1d489c","tid":736913,"uid":122